sources.description:
Suspense filled drama in the African jungle.
A goods trader in southern Africa aids a mysterious nun escape the clutches of a dangerous ivory and animal trafficker.

Original title: Africa Express (1975) AKA: Tropical Express

Watch this next: Safari Express (1976) https://youtu.be/VYIt1ZFbNu8

Director: Michele Lupo
Writers: Mario Amendola, Bruno Corbucci
Stars: Giuliano Gemma, Ursula Andress, Jack Palance
Genres: Action, Adventure, Comedy
